{"tid":2367144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★FBI：我們會運用所有合法權力和方法，瓦解任何嘗試或攻擊 拜登就職的人士","createTime":"2021-01-15T05:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T08:57:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2c7e65ef439cc777387fc4e748d911a22ed490","tid":2367144,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"全國廣播公司報道，最快本周六起有針對候任總統拜登就職禮的示威活動。聯邦調查局局長雷伊透露，正追蹤大批令人擔心的網上對話，包括呼籲由現在到就職禮之間發動武裝示威的言論。他表示已警告地方執法機關，衝擊國會山莊的行動會煽動有暴力傾向人士。  <br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦調查局局長雷伊稱：「外面的資訊量非常顯著，但我們一直盡快傳遞那些資訊向我們有關的執法和情報夥伴，若我們發現個別人士有暴力威脅，我們和我們的夥伴會運用所有合法權力和方法，瓦解任何嘗試或攻擊。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/6000ec8d34b0316b27332436/彭斯承強調確保政權安全交接-據報周六起有針對總統就職禮示威\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F6000ec8d34b0316b27332436%2F%E5%BD%AD%E6%96%AF%E6%89%BF%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E7%A2%BA%E4%BF%9D%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BA%A4%E6%8E%A5-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E8%B5%B7%E6%9C%89%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%B0%B1%E8%81%B7%E7%A6%AE%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=7839b79f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/6000ec8d34b0316b27332436/彭斯承強調確保政權安全交接-據報周六起有針對總統就職禮示威</a>"},{"pid":"aec459a9a1b59533b3bbc7a26bcd71672cea8620","tid":2367144,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926e222525e1fb813db951295b455716d34add13","tid":2367144,"uid":144626,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"